WEBVTT

2
00:00:01.070 --> 00:00:10.460
Zhang Peizan: Yes, I came back from walking the horses that day. Just when I walked to the garden, I heard the young lady and her fiancé talking.

3
00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:16.590
Zhang Peizan: She asked him to come to the garden in the middle of the night to get gold. Feelings of greed stirred in my heart at that moment.

4
00:00:16.590 --> 00:00:18.900
[Opera orchestra plays]

5
00:00:18.900 --> 00:00:29.000
♪ Chorus: He said that he stole a hairpin because he was greedy for gold, ♪

6
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:47.860
[Opera orchestra plays]

7
00:00:47.863 --> 00:00:53.113
♪ and quietly waited outside the garden for Xuechun. ♪

8
00:00:53.114 --> 00:01:00.354
♪ He clapped his hands three times so that the gate would open, ♪

9
00:01:00.354 --> 00:01:28.656
[Opera orchestra plays]

10
00:01:28.656 --> 00:01:34.300
♪ and he could exchange the hairpin for money without any hindrance. ♪

00:01:34.300 --> 00:01:46.800
Xuechun: Mr. Lin, you must not let my lady's kindness go to waste.

11
00:01:46.800 --> 00:01:48.900
Xuechun: It's getting late, please go back.

12
00:01:48.900 --> 00:01:51.000
[Opera orchestra plays]

13
00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:56.500
♪ Chorus: Flustered, legs trembling, he fell to the ground and ruined his plan. ♪

14
00:01:56.500 --> 00:01:57.600
Xuechun: Mr. Lin?

15
00:01:57.600 --> 00:01:58.000
[Sound effect: Gasp]

17
00:01:59.300 --> 00:02:00.000
Xuechun: Ah, it's you!

18
00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:05.800
Zhang Peizan: Don't shout. If you shout, I will kill you.

19
00:02:05.800 --> 00:02:11.000
♪ Chorus: One mistake of his caused her soul to travel to the underworld. ♪

20
00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:15.000
Xuechun: Help!

21
00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:15.500
[Music stops]

22
00:02:15.500 --> 00:02:26.900
Zhang Peizan: I had just hidden the knife and the gold when I saw the young master coming over — so he became my scapegoat!
